caption.text:
It's been a month since papa left me. I keep thinking about you even though it painfull. I’d give anything to relive those memories again. I really miss u. It hurts to think that you are not here anymore. Although I can’t help but smile with tears in my eyes to think of how we cherished each and every moment of our lives together when you were alive. I remember the joke you made to me. I remember you came to help me when the car broke down in the middle of the night. And you're not mad at me, you made jokes of it instead. You really were my savior that night. And always will.
And if I listen to the songs by Koes Plus or The Beatles, I always remember you and I really miss your beautiful voice. I miss the warm feeling when we sang together in the car.
Papa, how heartbroken i am and how much i miss you. I can't explain in words but my tears do. I still remember and will always remember your last hug, your last kiss and your last words to me. You died in a good day and smile because I know you were a good person. You are near even if i dont see you. You are with me even if you are far away. You are in my heart, in my thoughts, in my life, always.
Love you papa ❤
